## RESPONSE FORMAT DISCIPLINE (2026-03-01)
**MANDATORY FOR ALL RESPONSES - FOREVER**

Every response must follow this format:

```
YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS UTC
=============================================================
[Response content here]
=============================================================
```

**Example:**
```
2026-03-01 18:55:00 UTC
=============================================================
Your response text goes here.
=============================================================
```

**Why:** Traceability, structure, and temporal context for knowledge graph and relational memory systems.

**Applies to:** All responses in all projects, all future sessions, no exceptions.

